DTSTAMP:20260401T023626Z
DTSTART:20260411T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Description: Nomad Boxing Club is proud to host the PNW R
	egional Golden Gloves in Seattle for the first time ever\, bringing elite 
	amateur boxers from Washington\, Oregon\, and Alaska together for a two-da
	y championship event and the official pathway to the National Golden Glove
	s. Featuring a special appearance by boxing legend Roberto Durán\, this hi
	gh-energy weekend will showcase championship-level competition\, sellout c
	rowds\, and a historic moment for Nomad and the Seattle box ing community.
	\n\nNeighborhoods: Alki/Admiral\,Arbor Heights\,Ballard\,B eacon Hill\,Bel
	ltown\,Broadview/Bitter Lake\,Capitol Hill\,Cascade/Eastl ake/South Lake U
	nion\,Cedar Park/Meadowbrook\,Central Area/Squire Park\, Chinatown-Interna
	tional District\,Citywide\,Columbia City\,Delridge/Nort h Delridge\,Downto
	wn Commercial Core\,Duwamish/SODO\,East of Seattle\,Fa untleroy/Morgan Jun
	ction/Seaview\,First Hill\,Fremont\,Georgetown\,Green Lake\,Greenwood/Phin
	ney Ridge\,Haller Lake\,High Point\,Highland Park\, Interbay\,Judkins Park
