	 Springs\,Madison Park\,Madrona/Leschi\,Magnolia \,Miller Park\,Montlake/P
	ortage Bay\,Mt. Baker/North Rainier\,North Beach /Blue Ridge\,North Beacon
	 Hill/Jefferson Park\,North Capitol Hill\,North of Seattle\,Northgate/Mapl
	e Leaf\,Pioneer Square\,Queen Anne\,Rainier B each/Othello\,Ravenna/Bryant
