	Beacon Hill/New Holly\,South of Seattle\,So uth Park\,Sunset Hill/Loyal He
	ights\,University District\,Uptown\,Wallin gford\,Wedgwood/View Ridge\,Wes
	t of Seattle\,West Seattle Junction/Genes ee Hill\,Whittier Heights\n\nDON
	 Programs: Community Happenings\n\nEvent Types: Community\,Special Events\
	,Sports/Recreation\n\nAudience: All\n\nSponsoring Organization: Nomad Boxi
	ng Club\n\nContact: Manny Dunham\n\nContact Phone: 206-851-7269\n\nContact
	 Email: nomadboxingclub@gmail.com\n\nSite Contact Details: Manny Dunham\n\
	nPre-Register: Yes\n\nCost: $25-$200\n\nLink: https://nomadboxingclub.com/
